snippet.title: RobinHoodUK
snippet.description:
A channel for all UKIP news content and sometimes editorial content with rightwing, libertarian, classical liberal views by yours truly.
I pride myself on being the fastest uploader of everything UKIP.
by the way, if you want to contact me, just message me on facebook or twitter as i dont get notifications on youtube.
